# List All Domain

- Login to Plesk as admin
- Click on Domains from the left side menu of plesk
- The next window will show all existing domains on your server.

## How to Create New Domain

To add a domain for a new customer, create a customer account first. To add a domain for hosting your own website, create your own subscription first.

**Create A New Customer Account**

- Login to Plesk as admin
